s to be produced during warranty claim process.\n- Products without a serial number are not eligible for the extended warranty.\n- The extended warranty applies only to purchases made on the boAt website or boAt shopping app.\n- Full terms: [www.boat-lifestyle.com/pages/warranty](https://www.boat-lifestyle.com/pages/warranty)\n\n![](https://www.boat-lifestyle.com/cdn/shop/files/Group_334302_small.svg?v=1682336123)\n\n**GST**\n\nBilling\n\n![](https://www.boat-lifestyle.com/cdn/shop/files/Group_334303_small.svg?v=1682336123)\n\n**Free Express**\n\nDelivery\\*\n\n![](https://www.boat-lifestyle.com/cdn/shop/files/Group_334304_small.svg?v=1682336123)\n\n**7-day**\n\nReplacement\n\n100 Hours Playback\n\n![star](https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0057/8938/4802/files/star-5_20X20.png?v=1722331088)\n4.7\n\n\n92![verified reviews](https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0057/8938/4802/files/Mask_group-10.png?v=1677571152)\n\n![](https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0057/8938/4802/files/offer_4000e398-1550-49a4-8cf7-00ae10d6b50d.png?v=1726470069)\nEXTRA \u20b9100 OFF\n\n\ud83c\udf89 New Launch\n\n\n[![ Airdopes 181 Pro ](https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0057/8938/4802/files/AD_181_pro_1.png?v=1745234576&width=400)](https://www.boat-lifestyle.com/products/airdopes-181-pro-bluetooth-earbuds)\n\n[boAt Airdopes 181 Pro](https://www.boat-lifestyle.com/products/airdopes-181-pro-bluetooth-earbuds)\n\nSale price\u20b91,399\n\nRegular price\u20b94,990\n\n72% off\n\n+2+2\n\nBT Calling\n\n![star](https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0057/8938/4802/files/star-5_20X20.png?v=1722331088)\n4.9\n\n\n17![verified reviews](https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0057/8938/4802/files/Mask_group-10.png?v=1677571152)\n\n\ud83d\ude80 Bestseller\n\n\n[![ Wave Fury ](https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0057/8938/4802/files/Wave_Fury.webp?v=1702287204&width=400)](https://www.boat-lifestyle.com/products/wave-fury-bluetooth-smartwatch)\n\n[boAt Wave Fury](https://www.boat-lifestyle.com/products/wave-fury-bluetooth-smartwa